== 發行 ==
[[華納兄弟|華納兄弟]]原本將電影定於2015年11月25日上映<ref>{{cite web|title=Warner Bros Pushes Ben Affleck's 'Live By Night', Dates 'Midnight Special' & 3 Others|url=http://www.deadline.com/2014/05/warner-bros-pushes-ben-afflecks-live-by-night-dates-midnight-special-3-other-pics|accessdate=May 7, 2014|work=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|date=May 6, 2014|archive-date=2014-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140811192445/http://www.deadline.com/2014/05/warner-bros-pushes-ben-afflecks-live-by-night-dates-midnight-special-3-other-pics/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但在2015年7月時，就將日期延後至2016年3月18日<ref>{{cite web|title=Jeff Nichols’ ‘Midnight Special’ Pushed Into 2016|url=http://deadline.com/2015/07/midnight-special-release-date-jeff-nichols-joel-edgerton-kirsten-dunst-2016-1201486209|website=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|accessdate=31 July 2015|archive-date=2021-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210215092849/https://deadline.com/2015/07/midnight-special-release-date-jeff-nichols-joel-edgerton-kirsten-dunst-2016-1201486209/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

